For the H0DN combined value, Pop-I provides the high-statistical-weight backbone, while Pop-II + geometric measurements provide the systematic-cross-check. The combined H0DN value sits slightly below pure SH0ES at ~72.5, reflecting the modest pull from CCHP-style Pop-II measurements.\
